title: Mother of God, Kate Upton graces the COVERS of Sports Illustrated (12 GIFs)
text:
Via Sports Illustrated 
As if there aren’t enough reasons to adore Kate Upton , she goes and does something like this. AGAIN! This is her third time receiving the coveted cover shot of the Sports Illustrated swimsuit issue and with this being her third go around, she obviously gets three different covers for all of us to enjoy. Alright, let’s get to the good stuff. 2
